phrases: Now that we have found more members,
the Little Busters seems even more like a baseball team.
What the heck are you doing, Cuckoogayer?!
You are what I cannot respect.
But fun times like this cannot go on forever.
Kyousuke will graduate in less than a year.
It will not be long before we all go our separate ways.
That is your first strike ever, Rin.
You can call me the Fastball King from now on!
Hey, Rin-chan, why do not you eat with us?
It seems there is still no cure for Rin-kun's shyness.
Rin, what about the other girls?
Why do you guys have whiskers?
Do not they get in the way?
Like when you are drinking milk.
Is that something I should ask a cat?
Hey, Rin, why do not you try getting closer to the girls?
I have told you this plenty of times.
Masato, Kengo, and I cannot hang around with you forever.
When we all graduate, you will...
If we clear all the tasks, they said they would tell us the secret of the world.
We have a second task here.
Is there a problem with the cafeteria or something?
The croquette soba is super disgusting.
Is not that a matter of taste?
The cafeteria will be saved if the croquette soba is taken off the menu.
Then are there any other problems?
Why do not we ask the cafeteria ladies?
Have there been any problems with the cafeteria lately?
You all eat everything we make.
We are always happy about that.
But the croquette soba is disgusting!
We put that on the menu because some students requested it.
They serve them at some street stalls.
The croquettes get all mushy from the soup.
It seems you do not understand.
Those who do cannot live without it!
Slurping a croquette soaked mushy in soup!
The sparkling ace of the softball team, and...
So the person who requested croquette soba was...
It should be taken off the menu immediately!
Even though you like your tempura soba?
You were slurping up totally mushy tempura in soup.
Tempura tastes good when it is mushy!
It is not the same with croquettes!
I will not simply stand back while you insult the mushy croquettes I love so much!
How can you be so useless?!
Now we know who is right!
So how are we supposed to save the cafeteria?
Besides, we do not even know if there is a meaning to those letters in the first place.
We do not know who is writing them, either.
But if we clear all the tasks, they will tell us the secret of the world!
I wonder what the secret of the world is...
Rin was set on doing it until she learned the secret.
The same way she would keep buying snacks until she won a free one.
The way she did when she was young.
But what kind of secret could this world have?
All there is here is an unchanging everyday life.
If I had to name something that made me uneasy, it would be...
I do not know when I might fall asleep.
I am listening as hard as I can!
None of the cafeteria ladies are there.
The cafeteria ladies usually start preparing dinner around now,
but none of them are there.
There was one until a few minutes ago.
But she suddenly felt dizzy and went to the hospital.
The other ladies had emergencies, so they left early.
And there were already two out sick today, too.
All of them had to leave?
Either way, there is not anyone here to make dinner!
Where am I going to get dinner?!
My stomach's howling like a wild animal here!
If we do not start now, we will not make it in time!
There is a massive number of students in this school.
It is impossible for just the three of us to handle.
Once upon a time, there was a penguin.
I have a favor to ask!
You came all the way out here to ask for my help?
It must be quite a crisis.
Making dinner for every student in the school will be no easy feat.
But it seems you intend to do it.
This has to be the first time you have ever pulled everyone together.
Lennon's letter predicted that the cafeteria would have a problem like this.
How did the writer know that this would happen?
What are you going to do for this mission?
I am going to see it through with Rin, of course.
Then let us put our heads together for this.
Let us make a lot of yummy things!
Now that I have seen pretty girls in aprons, I am ready to do anything.
My, Anego, you look quite sexy as well.
I would do anything to have a wife like you making dinner for me!
So what do we do first?
Should not we figure out what we are serving first?
Pork cutlet meal, fillet cutlet meal, cutlet and rice meal,
combo meal, meat and vegetable cutlet meal...
We have to make all this?
Why not just pick three things to serve?
That is a pretty normal idea to get excited about.
It sounds like you were reading something.
And why was it in the form of a question?
We will have to make do with three dishes.
No, it is got to be cutlet!
Then how about fried shrimp and some cutlet for a combo dish?
Add some julienned cabbage, apple slices, and a bowl of miso,
and you have got a combo meal.
How about a rice ball meal, too?
We can put omelette on the side!
My grandpa told me to learn how to make Japanese-style omelettes,
so I learned how to make them back home.
Then you are in charge of omelettes, Kud.
We will need curry for the third dish.
Looks like it is all settled.
Alright, we do not have much time till dinner.
How do you make the shrimp and cutlet?!
You batter them with flour and bread crumbs, then fry them.
I will turn up the heat.
Haruka-kun, hurry up and make the daikon miso soup.
Let me show you a real move!
We will put out the stuff we have done first.
Why are you guys cooking dinner?
We just need to put them on the trays!
How many jellies do I get?
Hey, this is practically a cabbage meal!
I got a combo with curry!
Why does not mine have a jelly?!
We have got more over here!
This is the first time I have seen Rin so lively around other people.
But just one thing bothered me.
How did the writer of the letter Lennon brought us predict this crisis?
Who on Earth wrote that letter?
And then, it suddenly hit me again.
Just like always, it came without warning.
I was disconnected from this world.
I was all alone, as if the world had left me behind.
I could not tell how much time had passed or what time it was.
Just like the first time I had a sleep attack
Here is your fried combo meal!
You waited this long for me?
We could not end this mission without you.
Everyone worked really hard after that.
We managed to pull through in the end.
Let us get this party started!
A girl sitting quietly at lunch under a big tree.
Always reading a book under her parasol.
Find the book Miss Nishizono lost.
Why not just pick three things to serve?

Fly high, high into the sky,

Jump high, and raise your voice high,

kore kara hajimaru kibou to iu na no mirai wo

Those legs will keep on moving forward,
Those legs will keep on moving forward,
Even in the face of the oncoming grief
Even in the face of the oncoming grief
The sound of the bell echoing,
The sound of the bell echoing,
Those pieces we shared, one each
Those pieces we shared, one each
I hope tomorrow will be sunny
I hope tomorrow will be sunny
Can we go beyond the stars?
Can we go beyond the stars?
Walking, looking at the sky, a single light
Walking, looking at the sky, a single light
Even alone, on the face of the moon,
Even alone, on the face of the moon,
rasen no hate he kaketeyuku yo
Run right past the end of the circle
rasen no hate he kaketeyuku yo
Run right past the end of the circle
You will be able to smile after you cry,
You will be able to smile after you cry,
I said that because I know you can
I said that because I know you can

You will never forget our journey, even for a moment
bokura no tabi wasuretari shinai yo
